name: Pandatom
body:
### What is pandatom?
Collective / Group founded by Olli Suoranta and Tomi Ruusala that creates games more or less during their spare time.

### Projects
Currently developing Trojan Defense 2D

### Key people
- Olli Suoranta
- Tomi Ruusala
- Juho Saarelainen
- Petri Mölläri
